arts.ttl: Petar Musa scores, Jacob Jackson has 13 saves to help Dallas earn 1-1 draw with St. Louis City
arts.sum: Petar Musa scored the equalizer for FC Dallas in a 1-1 draw with St. Louis City and Jacob Jackson totaled 13 saves after goalkeeper Michael Collodi left the club shorthanded in the 16th minute on Saturday night. Célio Pompeu used an assist from Eduard Löwen to score in the 32nd minute and give St. Louis City (5-17-7) a 1-0 lead.
